ners of his eyes, as his father raped their sister over and over, the bedframe knocking against the wall in a sickening, rhythmic beat.\n", "embedding": [-0.07532558590173721, -0.015330018475651741, -0.028900742530822754, -0.028722813352942467, -0.019886979833245277, 0.015766846016049385, 0.0367971807718277, 0.02605084702372551, 0.05774252116680145, 0.009891477413475513, 0.038237012922763824, 0.07811740785837173, -0.0024414262734353542, 0.06181527301669121, 0.007042566780000925, -0.016341721639037132, -0.01735723577439785, 0.047387052327394485, -0.08822565525770187, 0.0907573401927948, 0.06715822219848633, 0.07782307267189026, 0.08906305581331253, -0.0503256693482399, -0.05013537034392357, 0.017835618928074837, -0.014623016119003296, -0.09138238430023193, -0.01701958104968071, -0.014563363045454025, -0.045878633856773376, -0.038004398345947266, -0.06621275842189789, -0.04335786774754524, -0.09310039132833481, 0.036089688539505005, 0.009411062113940716, 0.11077143251895905, 0.05700581148266792, 0.01973462849855423, -0.03716251254081726, 0.027512354776263237, -0.035981860011816025, 0.01415359228849411, 0.06592465937137604, 0.026151224970817566, -0.032641470432281494, -0.006461590062826872, 0.11826011538505554, -0.08044719696044922, -0.07756651192903519, 0.02557157725095749, 0.010652833618223667, -0.08389831334352493, -0.0026385257951915264, 0.004096624907106161, 0.08155708760023117, -0.03752739354968071, 0.02191237546503544, 0.023881254717707634, -0.013321722857654095, -0.04441303387284279, -0.020239435136318207, 0.07896855473518372, 0.09147268533706665, -0.0909007117152214, -0.0030943516176193953, -0.02033269964158535, -0.05229388549923897, 0.05983377993106842, -0.021000085398554802, -0.053948406130075455, -0.07821156829595566, -0.06274884939193726, -0.006510720122605562, -0.03891490027308464, -0.026737842708826065, -0.04921550676226616, 0.03856998309493065, 0.03898809850215912, -0.01863882504403591, -0.07165456563234329, 0.006656750105321407, 0.08218954503536224, 0.